<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8130012>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46–58. (46–50) Diaphorina gonzalezi: (46) male terminalia, lateral view; (47) paramere, inner surface, lateral view; (48) basal segment of aedeagus, lateral view; (49) distal segment of aedeagus, lateral view; (50) female terminalia, lateral view. (51–54) Arytaina insularis: (51) male terminalia, lateral view; (52) paramere, inner surface, lateral view; (53) distal segment of aedeagus, lateral view; (54) female terminalia, lateral view. (55–58) Arytaina meridionalis: (55) male terminalia, lateral view; (56) paramere, inner surface, lateral view; (57) distal segment of aedeagus, lateral view; (58) female terminalia, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8130012/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8130032>
    dc:description "FIGURES 118–131. (118–123) Strophingia canariensis: (118) head, dorsal view; (119) vertex, dorsal view; (120) last antennal segment; (121) antenna; (122) forewing; (123) forewing surface. (124) Strophingia paligera, forewing. (125–131) Diaphorina gonzalezi: (125) head, dorsal view; (126) genal processes, dorsal view; (127) antenna; (128) metacoxa; (129) forewing; (130) forewing, showing surface spinules and pattern; (131) female circumanal ring." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8130032/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8130054>
    dc:description "FIGURES 196–201. Fifth-instar immature; (196) Agonoscena atlantica; (197) Agonoscena sinuata; (198) Megadicrania tecticeps; (199) Strophingia canariensis; (200) Strophingia paligera; (201) Diaphorina gonzalezi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8130054/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8130072>
    dc:description "FIGURES 241–250. (241–244) Strophingia canariensis: (241, 242) adult, habitus; (241) lateral view; (242) dorsal view; (243, 244) fifth-instar immature. (245–250) Diaphorina gonzalezi: (245, 247) adult, habitus; (245) lateral view; (247) dorsal view; (246, 248–250) immatures." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8130072/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

